name: Fatman Scoop
summary: Rapper Fatman Scoop, known for his energetic performances, unfortunately passed away at the age of 53 after collapsing during a concert in Hamden, Connecticut. Witnesses reported that he suffered a medical emergency onstage and received CPR before being transported to the hospital. Despite efforts to save him, Scoop succumbed to his condition. The cause of the medical emergency is still under investigation, but authorities have confirmed his passing. News outlets such as TMZ, the New York Post, Eyewitness News 3, the New Haven Register, the Hollywood Reporter, CBS News, WTNH.com, syracuse.com, NBC Connecticut, and NBC News have reported on this tragic event, expressing condolences and sharing the news of Scoop's sudden passing.
